29.11.2023),</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">- Electric vehicle production was included among the production activities before the first publication date of the Communiqué (29.11.2023),</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">- Providing the conditions for gaining Turkish origin for the produced electric vehicles</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">It is reported that, with the approval of the Ministry dated 28/02/2025, it has been deemed appropriate to allow the import of the vehicles in question without the \"Permit Certificate\" specified in the Communiqué on the Importation of Certain Electric and Externally Rechargeable Hybrid Vehicles (Import: 2025/7) by registering their customs entry declarations (Free Circulation Entry Regime) provided that the conditions are met and the necessary supporting documents are submitted to the relevant Customs Administration.</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">I kindly request you to obtain information and take necessary action accordingly.</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: -webkit-center; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: -webkit-center; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: right; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=