rgin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: center; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><b style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important; font-weight: 400 !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">DISTRIBUTION LOCATIONS</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: -webkit-center; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: -webkit-center; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">As is known, the Communiqué on the Importation of Certain Electric Vehicles (Import: 2023/22) was published in the Official Gazette dated 29/11/2023 and numbered 32384, and for the import of electric vehicles within the scope of the Communiqué that do not originate from the European Union or countries with which a Free Trade Agreement has been signed, a \"Permit Certificate\" issued by the Ministry of Industry and Technology or the institution or organization authorized by it is required.</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">In this context, a Permit Certificate must be sought for Turkish origin goods produced in Free Zones within the scope of the Communiqué in force (Communiqué on the Importation of Certain Electric and Externally Rechargeable Hybrid Vehicles: 2025/7).</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">On the other hand, requests have been submitted to our Ministry for electric vehicles produced in the Free Zone and of Turkish origin to be exempt from the Communiqué.</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">As a result of the evaluations made, the companies operating in the Free Zones;</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">- Having been operating in Free Zones before the date of the first publication of the Communiqué (29.11.2023),</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">- Electric vehicle production was included among the production activities before the first publication date of the Communiqué (29.11.2023),</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">- Providing the conditions for gaining Turkish origin for the produced electric vehicles</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">If the conditions are met and the necessary supporting documents are submitted to the relevant Customs Administration, the customs entry declarations of the vehicles in question (Free Circulation Regime) will be registered and their import will be permitted without the \"Permit Certificate\" specified in the relevant Communiqué, with the Approval of the Ministry dated 28/02/2025.</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal; outline: 0px !important;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;color:black;=\"\" mso-font-kerning:0pt\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px !important;\">I present the information and what is necessary.</font></font><o:p style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.000